            "id": "4542801",
            "title": "First BanCorp. GAAP EPS of $0.55 beats by $0.04, revenue of $257.17M in-line",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>First BanCorp. <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20376819-first-bancorp-announces-earnings-for-the-quarter-and-year-ended-december-31-2025\">press release</a>  (FBP): Q4  GAAP EPS of $0.55 <font color=\"green\"> beats by $0.04</font>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $257.17M (+6.5% Y/Y) in-line.</li>\n<li>Adjusted pre-tax, pre-provision income $129.2 million compared to $121.5 million.</li>\n<li>Provision for credit losses – $23.0 million compared to $17.6 million.</li>\n<li>Core deposits (other than brokered and government deposits) – increased by $266.5 million to $13.1 billion, mainly in non-interest-bearing deposits in the Puerto Rico region.</li>\n<li>Allowance for credit losses (“ACL”) coverage ratio – amounted to 1.90%, compared to 1.89%.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
